'''Salem Caker''' (ilul deg [[1950]] deg Yiɛezzuzen, di tɣiwant n [[Larebɛa n At Yiraten]], [[Tizi Wezzu]]) d [[asnilsan]] linguiste [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|Aqbayli]] yerna d aselmad n [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tmaziɣt]] deg tesdawit deg [[Paris]] d [[Aix-en Provence]].  
	
Caker iqeddec deg [[INALCO|usudu aɣelnaw n tutlayin ed tɣermiwin Tisemranin]] (INALCO) id yezgan di [[Paris]] seg useggas n 1989, deg wemkan n [[André Basset]] d [[Lionel Galand]].

==Tameddurt Tasdawant==

Deg [[1973]] yewwi tafesna n duktuṛa deg [[tasnilest|tesnilst]] Tamatut. Sin akin seg [[1973]] ar [[1981]] yeqdec d aselmad deg tesdawit n temdint n Lezzayer. Deg 1978 yewwi duktuṛa niḍen deg [[Tasekla|tsekla]] d [ Tussniwin talsanin]]. Gar 1981 e 1989 yeqdec d aselmad deg temdint n [[Aix-en-Provence]] (deg tesdawit n Provence akked Wammas Aɣelnaw n Unadi Ussnan [CNRS]). 
Sakkin, deg 1990 yessbed-d Ammas n Unadi Amaziɣ "André Basset" deg [[Asudu|usudu]] n [[INALCO]]. Ma deg 2008 yebda iqeddec deg Usudu n Unadi ɣef Yimaḍalen Aserɣin d Yineslem n Aix-Provence. Salem Caker yura-d aṭas n yedlisen d tezrawin ɣef tesnilsit tamaziɣt. Daɣen, d netta ay d-yelhan s [[Tasedkalt Tamaziɣt|Tsedkalt Tamaziɣt]] (Encyclopédie Berbère) i d-itteffɣen g [[Fṛansa]]

